  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Enhancing Gender Mainstreaming and Socially Inclusive</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Consensus building and collaboration; Organizing one district level consultation/consensus building ;
Sensitization/awareness creation; Organizing a one-day sensitization workshop for 250 leaders of organized groups on issues related to district level elections, women and PwDs participation, possible election of MMDCEs and the referendum 
Capacity strengthening and education;  Organizing a 2-day workshop on leadership, advocacy, social mobilization and communication skills for 150 DA aspirants/representatives 
Community mobilization and awareness creation; Organizing 100 outreach programs on the importance of participation in the local level elections
Media / monitoring and evaluation; Organizing 5 media engagements to strengthen public awareness on the importance of citizens&#x2019; participation in local governance</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project seeks to improve on citizens&#x2019; responsiveness, increase citizens collaboration and inclusive participation in all forms of elections and referendums, particularly increasing the interest and enthusiasm of the youth, women and PwDs in local
governance processes for sustainable development.</narrative>
  </description>
